{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, as the year has increased, the digital literacy total score also has improved.A study with a population of undergraduate students of the Educational Science Faculty in Jordan revealed that the students had a medium level of awareness about computer technology ethics, and there were no significant differences in participants' levels of awareness regarding gender or year [48].",
    "Education about plagiarism among pharmacy and Nursing students showed an improved ability to identify plagiarism [49,50].",
    "Similarly, the students participating in our study showed that their digital ethics awareness regarding plagiarism, copyright and license, personal data protection, and ethics committee rose as their grade level increased.",
    "Our findings support the positive effect of education on digital ethics knowledge.In a study in Egypt, students were ethically aware of the importance of protecting information privacy showing their general sensitivity to this topic [51].",
    "However, this research indicated that students lack an ethical understanding of the propriety of copyright protection for software."
  ]
}